version 1.1.0.28 (2013-07-22)
	* open sourced

version 1.1.0.27 (2010-12-01)
	* demo dialog only on start and close

version 1.1.0.26 (2010-10-14)
	* added command line switch to select the license file
	* BUGFIX: when a custom directory was added, generating the HTML files crashed the application

version 1.1.0.25 (2010-06-10)
	* changed grid line style
	* BUGFIX: some <img> tags weren't being closed

version 1.1.0.23 (2010-04-05)
	* BUGFIX: "overflow: auto;" was causing scrollbars to appear on AP tableless layouts

version 1.1.0.22 (2010-03-31)
	* BUGFIX: when generating AP tableless sizes, the suffix "px" wasn't being added

version 1.1.0.21 (2009-11-28)
	* BUGFIX: image preview windows where incorrectly scrolling when receiving focus

version 1.1.0.18 (2009-04-08)
	* BUGFIX: assorted files weren't being saved correctly
	* Multiple XHTML compilance fixes
	* BUGFIX: MAP areas where named incorrectly

version 1.1.0.17 (2009-02-12)
	* BUGFIX: global areas were being allowed to have a DEFAULT config, which they shouldn't
	* Possibility to copy area configurations
	* BUGFIX: assorted files was outputting wrong URL path
	
version 1.1.0.14 (2008-11-30)
	* Translation support
	* pt_BR language translation
	* BUGFIX: BODY tag was outputting leftmargin 4 times
	* BUGFIX: BODY tag wasn't allowing override of leftmargin/topmargin/rightmargin/bottommargin
	* Support for BMP, TIFF and XPM output format
	* Dialog fixes for translations
	* pt_BR translation updates
	* Anchor tag smart tag appending support

version 1.1.0.9 (2008-11-05)
	* Per XHTML specification, all tag names should be lowercase - fixed

version 1.1.0.8 (2008-11-04)
	* BUGFIX: CSS file path handling was incorrect
	* BUGFIX: Global area dialog wasn't reflecting Alternate file setting
	* BUGFIX: Crash when deleting currently viewing VIEW
	* BUGFIX: Cannot select/insert lines connected to global areas main lines
	* Added 500% and 1000% zoom options to the image preview control
	* Option for AP tableless DIV styles to be at the top of page, instead of embedded into the DIV tags
	* Smart tag appending

version 1.1.0.2 (2008-10-30):
	* Added PNG 32 BIT as a default image format

version 1.1.0.1 (2008-10-29):
	* BUGFIX: mask was not being allowed to grow on the Mask dialog
	* BUGFIX: fixed exception bug in Unix

version 1.1.0.0 (2008-10-28):
	* Implemented AP TABLELESS output layout

version 1.0.3.0 (2008-10-25):
	* BUGFIX: when area RIGHT/BOTTOM was equals WIDTH/HEIGHT, was giving an "Invalid image" error message

version 1.0.2.0 (2008-10-17):
	* Area renaming menu shortcut
	* "Add view" wizard on "Project -> New"

version 1.0.1.4 (2008-10-15):
	* BUGFIX: root mask wasn't allowing increasing its size
	
version 1.0.1.1 (2008-09-30):
	* initial BETA version - released to BETA testers only

